    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Evidence from PIV validation and Monte Carlo UQ studies supports the overall assessment. The mesh-independence claim for VAD hemolysis predictions is considered established based on the three-level GCI study documented in the assessment report. Achieved levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors; however, the package is accepted as a complete credibility evidence submission pending remediation actions.",
